cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.AR 

This paper is about detecting data races in parallel software, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the incorporation of data and control dependence, which is related to program analysis (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach using real Java programs, which is related to architecture (cs.AR).
